    <div class="faq rv">
      <div class="qa"><button aria-expanded="false">Do I own the code?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="a"><p>Yes — completely. Every engagement ends with a full transfer: source code, credentials, infrastructure access, and technical documentation. No licensing, no platform lock-in, no dependency on us.</p></div></div>
      <div class="qa"><button aria-expanded="false">How do you deliver this fast?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="a"><p>Fixed scope, senior engineering, and a production-hardened toolchain. One architect owns your system end-to-end — no handoffs, no committees, and no discovery phases that bill by the hour.</p></div></div>
      <div class="qa"><button aria-expanded="false">What happens after launch?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="a"><p>You hold the source code. Any qualified engineer can extend it. If you want us to continue building, we offer month-to-month engineering support with no minimums and no lock-in.</p></div></div>
      <div class="qa"><button aria-expanded="false">What is the technology stack?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="a"><p>React, Next.js, and TypeScript on the front; Node.js and PostgreSQL behind it — statically typed, documented, and deployed on auto-scaling cloud infrastructure with CI/CD from day one.</p></div></div>
      <div class="qa"><button aria-expanded="false">Can you integrate with our existing systems?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="a"><p>Yes. If it exposes an endpoint, we can integrate with it — CRMs, payment processors, calendars, messaging platforms, legacy databases, and custom middleware where none exists.</p></div></div>
      <div class="qa"><button aria-expanded="false">How long does a project take?<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="a"><p>Foundation systems ship in 3–7 days, Professional builds in 5–10, and Enterprise platforms in 10–21. Your complete architecture is in your hands within 24 hours of the first call.</p></div></div>
